<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Reviewer Load Dashboard</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 64 64'><rect width='64' height='64' rx='12' fill='%23FF0039'/><text x='32' y='49' font-family='-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif' font-weight='900' font-size='52' fill='white' text-anchor='middle'>m</text></svg>">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght,SOFT@0,9..144,300..900,0..100;1,9..144,300..900,0..100&family=Instrument+Sans:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --paper: #FAF7F0;
    --paper-warm: #F2EBDC;
    --ink: #16110D;
    --ink-soft: #3B342D;
    --muted: #8B8378;
    --rule: #E6DECD;
    --rule-soft: #F0E9D9;
    --surface: #FFFFFF;
    --red: #FF0039;
    --red-deep: #B3002A;

    /* legacy token aliases retained in case any inline reference uses them */
    --bg: var(--paper);
    --fg: var(--ink);
    --card: var(--surface);
    --accent: var(--red);
    --warn: var(--red);
    --pill: var(--paper-warm);
    --pill-active: var(--ink);
    --pill-active-fg: var(--paper);

    --serif: 'Fraunces', 'Iowan Old Style', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, monospace;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  }

  /* Sticky top bar — header + view selector pinned together */
  .top-bar {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: var(--paper);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  header {
    padding: 22px 40px 10px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 90, "wght" 500, "SOFT" 30;
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  header h1 a {
    color: var(--muted) !important;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    opacity: 1 !important;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 60, "wght" 400;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-right: 12px !important;
    vertical-align: 3px;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    transition: color 0.15s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  header h1 a:hover { color: var(--red) !important; }
  header h1 #header-group {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--red);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 90, "wght" 500, "SOFT" 100;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  header .meta {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* View / period selector — text tabs with red underline */
  .toggle-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline;
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2px 40px 12px;
  }
  .toggle-group { display: flex; }
  .toggle-sep {
    width: 1px; height: 11px;
    background: var(--rule);
    margin: 5px 14px;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .toggle-bar button {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: none;
    padding: 4px 0;
    margin-right: 20px;
    font: inherit;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .toggle-bar button::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -2px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--red);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.22s ease;
  }
  .toggle-bar button:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .toggle-bar button.active {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .toggle-bar button.active::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  main {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 18px 40px 48px;
  }

  /* Page divider — used for the inline phab-section H2 dividers */
  .page-divider {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 60, "wght" 500, "SOFT" 30;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
    padding: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .page-divider em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--red);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 60, "wght" 500, "SOFT" 100;
  }

  section {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 16px 20px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }
  section h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30, "wght" 600, "SOFT" 30;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  section h2 .info { vertical-align: middle; }

  /* Small marginal § marker beside each section, like a printed footnote */
  section::before {
    content: '§';
    position: absolute;
    left: -30px; top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--rule);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30, "wght" 400, "SOFT" 100;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1340px) { section::before { display: none; } }

  /* Stats grid — bordered tiles using gap+background hairline trick */
  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(170px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .stat {
    padding: 11px 14px 13px;
    background: var(--surface);
    position: relative;
  }
  .stat .label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .stat .value {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72, "wght" 500, "SOFT" 20;
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 6px;
    letter-spacing: -0.022em;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-feature-settings: "tnum", "lnum";
  }
  .stat .sub {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .stat.expandable {
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .stat.expandable:hover { background: var(--paper); }
  .stat.expandable .label::after {
    content: " →";
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 10px;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }
  .stat.expandable.is-open { background: var(--paper-warm); }
  .stat.expandable.is-open .label::after { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .stat.expandable .hint {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 8.5px;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-top: 5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Nested detail (subdir breakdown) — appears below summary tiles */
  .nested-detail {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    padding: 14px 20px 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
    border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nested-detail h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 24, "wght" 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .nested-detail .chart-box.square { max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .nested-detail .close-detail {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 14px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px; padding: 4px 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .nested-detail .close-detail:hover {
    border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red);
  }

  /* Sub-details — expandable table-of-patches list */
  .sub-details {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    padding: 10px 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .sub-details > summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
    padding: 4px 0;
  }
  .sub-details > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .sub-details > summary::before {
    content: "▸ "; color: var(--red);
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.15s;
    width: 1em;
  }
  .sub-details[open] > summary::before { content: "▾ "; }
  .sub-details table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .sub-details th, .sub-details td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 9px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .sub-details th {
    background: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .sub-details td.subject { max-width: 380px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
  .sub-details td.subdir-cell {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    color: var(--red-deep);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Back to top — fixed bottom right */
  #back-to-top {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 28px; right: 28px;
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-size: 18px; line-height: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(22, 17, 13, 0.18);
    opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;
    transform: translateY(6px);
    transition: opacity 0.18s, transform 0.18s, visibility 0.18s,
                background 0.18s, border-color 0.18s;
    z-index: 200;
  }
  #back-to-top.is-visible {
    opacity: 1; visibility: visible;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  #back-to-top:hover {
    background: var(--red);
    border-color: var(--red);
  }
  #back-to-top:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--red);
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }

  /* Chart boxes */
  .chart-box { position: relative; height: 280px; }
  .chart-box.tall { height: 380px; }
  .chart-box.square { height: 280px; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: 20px; align-items: center; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* Tables */
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    table-layout: fixed;
  }
  th, td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  th {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  th.num, td.num {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }
  #queue-table td.title { word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
  #queue-table a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }
  #queue-table a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
    border-bottom-color: var(--red);
  }
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  th.sortable { cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
  th.sortable:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  th.sortable.active-sort { color: var(--red); }
  th.sortable.active-sort::after {
    content: " ↓";
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .footer-note {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 12, "wght" 400, "SOFT" 50;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Info chip + tooltip */
  .info {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-left: 6px;
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    font-size: 10px; line-height: 14px; text-align: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--paper-warm); color: var(--muted);
    cursor: help;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 9, "wght" 600;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    vertical-align: 1px;
  }
  .info::before { content: "i"; }
  .info:hover { background: var(--red); color: var(--paper); }
  section h2 .info { vertical-align: middle; }

  .tip-floating {
    position: fixed; display: none;
    max-width: 280px;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
    padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
    z-index: 1000;
    pointer-events: none;
    white-space: normal;
  }

  /* View axis: data-view ∈ {team, member, queue} */
  body[data-view="team"]    .member-only, body[data-view="team"]    .queue-only,
  body[data-view="member"]  .team-only,   body[data-view="member"]  .queue-only,
  body[data-view="queue"]   .team-only,   body[data-view="queue"]   .member-only
    { display: none !important; }

  body[data-view="team"][data-period="total"]  .weekly-only,
  body[data-view="team"][data-period="weekly"] .total-only { display: none !important; }

  body[data-view="member"] .toggle-group-period, body[data-view="member"] .toggle-sep,
  body[data-view="queue"]  .toggle-group-period, body[data-view="queue"]  .toggle-sep
    { display: none; }

  /* Profile select */
  .profile-select {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .profile-select:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .profile-select:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--red);
    outline-offset: 1px;
    border-color: var(--red);
  }
  .profile-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .queue-intro {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body data-view="team" data-period="total">

<div class="top-bar">
  <header>
    <h1><a href="../index.html" title="Back to team picker">←</a>Reviewer Load <span style="color: var(--muted); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 110, 'wght' 300; font-style: italic;">·</span> <span id="header-group"></span></h1>
    <div class="meta" id="header-meta"></div>
  </header>
  <nav class="toggle-bar" aria-label="View and period selectors">
    <div class="toggle-group" role="tablist" aria-label="View">
      <button data-view="team"   class="active" type="button">Team View</button>
      <button data-view="member" type="button">Member View</button>
      <button data-view="queue"  type="button">Wait Queue</button>
    </div>
    <div class="toggle-sep" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="toggle-group toggle-group-period" role="tablist" aria-label="Period">
      <button data-period="total"  class="active" type="button">6-Month</button>
      <button data-period="weekly" type="button">Per-Week</button>
    </div>
  </nav>
</div>

<main>
<!-- Sentinel watched by IntersectionObserver to toggle the
     back-to-top button. When this leaves the viewport (the user
     has scrolled past the top of <main>), the button fades in. -->
<div id="top-sentinel" aria-hidden="true" style="height:1px"></div>

<!-- ============= TEAM / 6-MONTH ============= -->
<div class="team-only total-only">

  <section>
    <h2>Summary (6-month window)</h2>
    <div class="summary-grid" id="summary-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <div id="landed-without-review-section" class="nested-detail" style="display:none">
    <button type="button" class="close-detail" id="close-no-team-review" aria-label="Collapse details">✕ Collapse</button>
    <h3>Breakdown by primary subdirectory <span class="info" data-tip="Each patch is bucketed by the subdirectory under the team's owned paths it changes the most files in. Click a legend entry to hide/show that slice."></span></h3>
    <div class="chart-box square"><canvas id="chart-no-team-review"></canvas></div>
    <div class="footer-note">Helps tell apart real team-scope bypasses from patches that live in the team's tree but are owned by an adjacent team.</div>
    <details class="sub-details" id="no-team-review-list-details">
      <summary>Full patch list (<span id="no-team-review-list-count">0</span>)</summary>
      <div id="no-team-review-list-container"></div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>Concentration metrics (6-month totals)</h2>
    <div class="summary-grid" id="concentration-grid"></div>
    <div class="footer-note">Gini: 0 = perfectly even, 1 = one person does everything. Bus factor = smallest # of members whose absence leaves &gt;50% uncovered. All percentages are over reviews by listed members only.</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Within-group distribution — listed members only <span class="info" data-tip="Reviews per listed member on patches tagged with the team's review group. Only roster members are counted; outside reviewers are excluded."></span></h2>
    <div class="split">
      <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chart-distribution"></canvas></div>
      <div class="chart-box square"><canvas id="chart-distribution-pie"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sole-reviewer patches (bus-factor risk) <span class="info" data-tip="Patches with exactly one reviewer named (a listed member, no group). Highest single-point-of-failure risk per person."></span></h2>
    <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chart-sole"></canvas></div>
    <div class="footer-note">Patches with exactly one reviewer (a listed member, no group tagged).</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Total reviews per member (sole + co-reviewed, any tag) <span class="info" data-tip="All in-scope patches each member reviewed, split by whether the patch was tagged with the team's review group (blue, &quot;our&quot; work) or not (gray, drive-by / cross-domain)."></span></h2>
    <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chart-total-reviews"></canvas></div>
    <div class="footer-note">All in-scope patches each member reviewed in the window. Blue = patches tagged with the team's review group; gray = other in-scope patches (drive-by / cross-domain reviews).</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Top patch authors <span class="info" data-tip="Authors of in-scope patches in the window. Aliases collapsed (e.g. alastor0325 / alwu → Alastor Wu)."></span></h2>
    <div class="chart-box tall"><canvas id="chart-authors"></canvas></div>
    <div class="footer-note">All authors of in-scope patches in the window (any reviewer).</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Author &rarr; reviewer mapping (top authors only) <span class="info" data-tip="For each top author, stacked bar of which listed members reviewed their patches. Non-member reviews are not shown."></span></h2>
    <div class="chart-box tall"><canvas id="chart-author-reviewer"></canvas></div>
    <div class="footer-note">For each author's patches, which listed members reviewed them. Bars only count reviews by members; non-member reviews don't appear here.</div>
  </section>

</div>

<!-- ============= TEAM / PER-WEEK ============= -->
<div class="team-only weekly-only">

  <section>
    <h2>Latest week snapshot — <span id="weekly-summary-label"></span></h2>
    <div class="summary-grid" id="weekly-summary-grid"></div>
    <div class="footer-note">"This week" = the most recent ISO week with any landing in the dataset.</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Concentration metrics — latest week</h2>
    <div class="summary-grid" id="weekly-concentration-grid"></div>
    <div class="footer-note">Same metrics as the 6-month view, computed over the latest week's group-tagged reviews only. Use the deltas to spot drift.</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Weekly trend — listed members <span class="info" data-tip="Reviews per ISO week for every listed member, ordered top-to-bottom in the legend by total reviews over the 6-month window. Click a name in the legend to hide/show its line."></span></h2>
    <div class="chart-box tall"><canvas id="chart-trend-all"></canvas></div>
